    "content": "<h1>mpatanishi</h1><h2>Ufafanuzi:</h2><p>Mpatanishi ni mtu anayesaidia watu wawili au zaidi kutatua mizozo au migogoro yao kwa pamoja. Anawasaidia kufikia makubaliano.</p><ul><li><p>Kwa sababu watu wamefanya dhambi, wamekuwa maadui wa Mungu na wanastahili ghadhabu na adhabu yake. Dhambi imevunja uhusiano kati ya Mungu na watu wake.</p></li><li><p>Yesu ni mpatanishi kati ya Mungu Baba na watu wake, akirejesha uhusiano huo uliovunjika kupitia kifo chake kama fidia ya dhambi zao.</p></li></ul><h2>Mapendekezo ya Tafsiri:</h2><ul><li><p>Njia za kutafsiri &quot;mpatanishi&quot; zinaweza kuwa &quot;mtu wa kati,&quot; &quot;upatanisho,&quot; au &quot;mtu anayeleta amani.&quot;</p></li><li><p>Linganisha neno hili na jinsi neno &quot;kuhani&quot; linavyotafsiriwa. Ingekuwa bora ikiwa neno &quot;mpatanishi&quot; lingetafsiriwa tofauti.</p></li></ul><p>(Tazama pia: <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"26121\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">mchungaji</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"26160\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">upatanisho</span>)</p><h2>Marejeleo ya Biblia:</h2><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1 Timotheo 2:5</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:20\">Wagalatia 3:20</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:6\">Waebrania 8:6</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:24\">Waebrania 12:24</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:14\">Luka 12:14</a></p></li></ul><h2>Data ya Neno:</h2><ul><li><p>Strong&apos;s: H3887, G33120, G33160</p></li></ul>",
